*Pukovnik* je bio na čelu vojske. (The colonel was in charge of the army.)

*Pukovnik* je želeo da se pridruži vojsci. (The colonel wanted to join the army.)

Vojska je bila pod vođstvom *pukovnika*. (The army was under the command of the colonel.)

*Pukovnik* je imao puno iskustva u vojsci. (The colonel had a lot of experience in the army.)

*Pukovnik* je bio poštovan od strane vojnika. (The colonel was respected by the soldiers.)